{"tid":2088645,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"(非舊聞）安全專家發現 PS2 DVD視頻播放漏洞允許其運行任何遊戲","createTime":"2020-07-01T08:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T05:47:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f4a4b276fda42f3212c143b64759777b9ef3d65c","tid":2088645,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T08:45:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.technadu.com/security-expert-discovered-flaw-ps2-gives-way-play-any-game/106056/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.technadu.com%2Fsecurity-expert-discovered-flaw-ps2-gives-way-play-any-game%2F106056%2F&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbhBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=e99f2d98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.technadu.com/security-expert-discovered-flaw-ps2-gives-way-play-any-game/106056/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cturt.github.io/freedvdboot.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcturt.github.io%2Ffreedvdboot.html&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbhBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=86179dfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cturt.github.io/freedvdboot.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/CTurt/FreeDVDBoot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FCTurt%2FFreeDVDBoot&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbhBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=e86c0749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/CTurt/FreeDVDBoot</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ez0y-hz3VuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fez0y-hz3VuM&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbhBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=745f5937\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ez0y-hz3VuM</a><br />\n<br />\n名叫 Cturt 的安全工程師找到了 PS2 的一個漏洞，允許其運行任何遊戲，不是指盜-版光盤遊戲，而是任何能刻錄在 DVD 光盤上的遊戲，包括不是設計運行在 PS 平台上的如超級馬里奧。Cturt 聲稱無需任何硬件上的修改或任何類型的 Mod，唯一需要的就是設法觸發一個讀溢出漏洞。他的方法被稱為 FreeDVDBoot，其技術細節發佈在 GitHub 上。他認為類似的漏洞也能工作在 PS 一代以及 PS3 和 PS4 上，PS4 之前的遊戲機早已不再更新，新漏洞的發現也許能讓這些舊遊戲機煥發新春。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/CTurtE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCTurtE&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbhBk8ry%2Bv12G5j1RUyKX8i0%3D&h=8b856c47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/CTurtE</a><br />\n目前已經支持3.11J\\E\\U以及3.04，實際利用ESR也可以運行商業遊戲備份。"},{"pid":"5b10ab24f1e26a0485bbff3c27fade1177b13cd1","tid":2088645,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T09:14:32.000Z","msg":"Wow 外星科技<br />\n<br />\nPs5 仲有無得喺香港賣"},{"pid":"fcf82f610746c471f30717b0a9a3f22d6f72369a","tid":2088645,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:14:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f06c8f9c918b2dbd79a8e04493028fc7d9fc18e","tid":2088645,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"允許其運行任何遊戲，不是指盜-版光盤遊戲，而是任何能刻錄在 DVD 光盤上的遊戲<br />\n<br />\nPS2 可以行PS4 DVD game?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0dbf51e3ff7de31f46fe05f66603c5324e32bc7","tid":2088645,"uid":107023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:23:07.000Z","msg":"即係令佢個os行佢睇得明的program ?"},{"pid":"2e1fa9c490567dadc64ca7526e0b426c2bdc76b6","tid":2088645,"uid":3677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f06c8f9c918b2dbd79a8e04493028fc7d9fc18e","tid":2088645,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:18:46.000Z","msg":"允許其運行任何遊戲，不是指盜-版光盤遊戲，而是任何能刻錄在 DVD 光盤上的遊戲<br />\n<br />\nPS2 可以行PS4 DVD game?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"ps3打後行緊blu-ray <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810e06ce1325d909b0413be67fead54b376ebdcb","tid":2088645,"uid":98795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T17:31:43.000Z","msg":"床下底仲有部PS2 9000機<br />\n可以玩到啲咩驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf5e7f9dc7d3b00d3e4